resources like a single printer for the

00:00:30.445 --> 00:00:36.295
whole office, the internet connection,
or to just exchange files and messages.

00:00:36.865 --> 00:00:42.144
These connections can be physical
using wires and cables, or they can be

00:00:42.144 --> 00:00:44.700
wireless using magic signals in the air.

00:00:45.010 --> 00:00:51.460
What we call wifi, the main purpose,
the big idea is to get all these

00:00:51.460 --> 00:00:57.459
devices to cooperate and work together
as one big, happy, efficient family.

